class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-66005"></a> and <span 
class="cmbx-10">financebars (p.</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">&#x00A0;</span><a 
href="#x1-71000II"><span 
class="cmbx-10">62</span><!--tex4ht:ref: financebars --></a><span 
class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-66006"></a>. See also the
