<!--l. 3427--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 3430--><p class="noindent" >This will produce a plot with clusters of two boxes (vertical bars) centered at each integral value on the x axis. If the
first column of the input file contains labels, they may be placed along the x-axis using the variant
                                                                                         
                                                                                         
command
<!--l. 3435--><p class="noindent" ><pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
