class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;"Times,8"</span>
<!--l. 3744--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 3747--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">labels </span>style can also be used in 3D plots. In this case four input column specifiers are required, corresponding
