<h3 class="likesectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-104000III"></a>Evaluate</h3>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-204"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-104001"></a>
<!--l. 4345--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">evaluate </span>command executes the commands given as an argument string. Newline characters are not allowed
within the string.
<!--l. 4348--><p class="noindent" >Syntax: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;eval</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;&#x003C;string</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;expression&#x003E;</span>
<!--l. 4352--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 4355--><p class="noindent" >This is especially useful for a repetition of similar commands.
<!--l. 4357--><p class="noindent" >Example: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
