class="cmbx-10">_incr</span><span 
class="cmmi-10">&#x003E;</span>.
<!--l. 5887--><p class="noindent" >The first datum in each block is numbered &#8217;0&#8217;, as is the first block in the file.
<!--l. 5890--><p class="noindent" >Note that records containing unplottable information are counted.
<!--l. 5892--><p class="noindent" >Any of the numbers can be omitted; the increments default to unity, the start values to the first point or
block, and the end values to the last point or block. If <span 
class="cmbx-10">every </span>is not specified, all points in all lines are
plotted.
