than space-separated columns. The same result could be achieved by specifying <span 
class="cmbx-10">set datafile separator </span><span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">,</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>.
<pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
