href="#x1-264000III"><span 
class="cmbx-10">182</span><!--tex4ht:ref: show plot --></a><span 
class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-186005"></a> to show the whole current plotting command, and the possibility to copy it into the
<span 
