<!--l. 10671--><p class="noindent" >The effects of <span 
class="cmbx-10">mapping </span>can be duplicated with the <span 
class="cmbx-10">using </span>filter on the <span 
class="cmbx-10">splot </span>command, but <span 
class="cmbx-10">mapping </span>may be more
convenient if many data files are to be processed. However even if <span 
class="cmbx-10">mapping </span>is used, <span 
class="cmbx-10">using </span>may still be necessary if
the data in the file are not in the required order.
<!--l. 10676--><p class="noindent" ><span 
class="cmbx-10">mapping </span>has no effect on <span 
class="cmbx-10">plot</span>.
