<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-252000III"></a>My2tics</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-500"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-252001"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-252002"></a>
<!--l. 11101--><p class="noindent" >Minor tic marks along the y2 (right-hand) axis are controlled by <span 
class="cmbx-10">set my2tics</span>. Please see <span 
class="cmbx-10">set mxtics</span>
<span 
class="cmbx-10">(p.</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">&#x00A0;</span><a 
href="#x1-251000III"><span 
class="cmbx-10">175</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set mxtics --></a><span 
class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-252003"></a>.
