<!--l. 11992--><p class="noindent" >Use <span 
class="cmbx-10">positive </span>and <span 
class="cmbx-10">negative </span>to invert the figure colors.
<!--l. 11996--><p class="noindent" >Note that it is possible to find a set of the best matching rgbformulae for any other color scheme by the command
<pre class="prettyprint">
