class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;palette</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;functions</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;gray**0.64,</span><span 
