<!--l. 12976--><p class="noindent" >By default, successive plots within the same graph will use successive linetypes from the default set for the current
terminal type. However, choosing <span 
class="cmbx-10">set style increment user </span>allows you to step through the user-defined line styles
rather than through the default linetypes.
<!--l. 12981--><p class="noindent" >Example:
