 id="Q1-1-642"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-323001"></a>
<!--l. 13806--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">set x2data </span>command sets data on the x2 (top) axis to timeseries (dates/times). Please see <span 
class="cmbx-10">set xdata</span>
<span 
