 id="dx1-325001"></a>
<!--l. 13830--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">set x2label </span>command sets the label for the x2 (top) axis. Please see <span 
class="cmbx-10">set xlabel (p.</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">&#x00A0;</span><a 
href="#x1-332000III"><span 
class="cmbx-10">217</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set xlabel --></a><span 
class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-325002"></a>.
