class="cmbx-10">set xzeroaxis; set yzeroaxis</span>. Note that the z-axis must be set separately using <span 
class="cmbx-10">set</span>
<span 
class="cmbx-10">zzeroaxis</span>.
<!--l. 14831--><p class="noindent" >Examples:
<!--l. 14833--><p class="noindent" >To simply have the y=0 axis drawn visibly:
