<!--l. 16296--><p class="noindent" >The first thirteen of these fonts are required for WebCGM. The Microsoft Office CGM import filter implements the
13 standard fonts listed above, and also &#8217;ZapfDingbats&#8217; and &#8217;Script&#8217;. However, the script font may only be accessed
under the name &#8217;15&#8217;. For more on Microsoft import filter font substitutions, check its help file which you may find
here: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;C:\Program</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;Files\Microsoft</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;Office\Office\Cgmimp32.hlp</span>
<!--l. 16305--><p class="noindent" ></pre> and/or its configuration file, which you may find here: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;C:\Program</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;Files\Common</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;Files\Microsoft</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;Shared\Grphflt\Cgmimp32.cfg</span>
<!--l. 16311--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 16314--><p class="noindent" >In the <span 
class="cmbx-10">set term </span>command, you may specify a font name which does not appear in the default font table. In that
case, a new font table is constructed with the specified font as its first entry. You must ensure that the spelling,
capitalization, and spacing of the name are appropriate for the application that will read the CGM file. (Gnuplot
and any MIL-D-28003A compliant application ignore case in font names.) If you need to add several new fonts, use
several <span 
class="cmbx-10">set term </span>commands.
<!--l. 16322--><p class="noindent" >Example: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;terminal</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;cgm</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;&#8217;Old</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;English&#8217;</span>
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><br /><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;terminal</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;cgm</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;&#8217;Tengwar&#8217;</span>
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><br /><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;terminal</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;cgm</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;&#8217;Arabic&#8217;</span>
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><br /><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
