class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;enhanced</span>
<!--l. 17599--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 17602--><p class="noindent" >Searches for a scalable font with face name &#8217;arial&#8217; and sets the font size to 14pt. Please see <span 
class="cmbx-10">fonts (p.</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">&#x00A0;</span><a 
href="#x1-36000I"><span 
class="cmbx-10">37</span><!--tex4ht:ref: fonts --></a><span 
class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-424001"></a>
for details of how the font search is done. Because this is a scalable font, we can use enhanced text
mode.
<!--l. 17607--><p class="noindent" ><pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;term</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;gif</span><span 
