class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;copy</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;"trig.pic"</span>
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><br /><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;.PE</span>
<!--l. 17706--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-426000IV"></a>Grass</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-847"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-426001"></a>
<!--l. 17717--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">grass </span>terminal driver gives <span 
class="cmbx-10">gnuplot </span>capabilities to users of the GRASS geographic information system.
Contact grassp-list@moon.cecer.army.mil for more information. Pages are written to the current frame of the
GRASS Graphics Window. There are no options.
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-427000IV"></a>Hp2623a</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-849"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-427001"></a>
<!--l. 17730--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">hp2623a </span>terminal driver supports the Hewlett Packard HP2623A. It has no options.
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-428000IV"></a>Hp2648</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-851"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-428001"></a>
<!--l. 17741--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">hp2648 </span>terminal driver supports the Hewlett Packard HP2647 and HP2648. It has no options.
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-429000IV"></a>Hp500c</h4>
                                                                                         
                                                                                         
<a 
 id="Q1-1-853"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-429001"></a>
<!--l. 17752--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">hp500c </span>terminal driver supports the Hewlett Packard HP DeskJet 500c. It has options for resolution and
compression.
<!--l. 17755--><p class="noindent" >Syntax: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;terminal</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;hp500c</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;{&#x003C;res&#x003E;}</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;{&#x003C;comp&#x003E;}</span>
<!--l. 17759--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 17762--><p class="noindent" >where <span 
class="cmbx-10">res </span>can be 75, 100, 150 or 300 dots per inch and <span 
class="cmbx-10">comp </span>can be <span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>rle<span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>, or <span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>tiff<span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>. Any other inputs are replaced
by the defaults, which are 75 dpi and no compression. Rasterization at the higher resolutions may require a large
amount of memory.
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-430000IV"></a>Hpgl</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-855"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-430001"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-430002"></a>
<!--l. 17782--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">hpgl </span>driver produces HPGL output for devices like the HP7475A plotter. There are two options which can be
set: the number of pens and <span 
class="cmbx-10">eject</span>, which tells the plotter to eject a page when done. The default is to use 6 pens
and not to eject the page when done.
<!--l. 17787--><p class="noindent" >The international character sets ISO-8859-1 and CP850 are recognized via <span 
class="cmbx-10">set encoding iso</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">_8859</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">_1 </span>or <span 
class="cmbx-10">set</span>
<span 
class="cmbx-10">encoding cp850 </span>(see <span 
class="cmbx-10">set encoding (p.</span><span 
class="cmbx-10">&#x00A0;</span><a 
href="#x1-218000III"><span 
class="cmbx-10">150</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set encoding --></a><span 
class="cmbx-10">)</span><a 
 id="dx1-430003"></a> for details).
<!--l. 17791--><p class="noindent" >Syntax: <pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;terminal</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;hpgl</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;{&#x003C;number_of_pens&#x003E;}</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;{eject}</span>
<!--l. 17795--><p class="noindent" ></pre>
<!--l. 17798--><p class="noindent" >The selection
<!--l. 17801--><p class="noindent" ><pre class="prettyprint">
<span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;set</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;terminal</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;hpgl</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;8</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;eject</span>
