class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;{size</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;&#x003C;XX&#x003E;{unit},</span><span 
class="cmtt-10">&#x00A0;&#x003C;YY&#x003E;{unit}}</span><span 
