<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-437000IV"></a>Linux</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-869"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-437001"></a>
<!--l. 18120--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">linux </span>driver has no additional options to specify. It looks at the environment variable GSVGAMODE for the
default mode; if not set, it uses 1024x768x256 as default mode or, if that is not possible, 640x480x16 (standard
VGA).
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
