<a 
 id="Q1-1-871"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-438001"></a>
<!--l. 18133--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">lua </span>generic terminal driver works in conjunction with an external Lua script to create a target-specific plot file.
Currently the only supported target is TikZ -<span 
class="cmmi-10">&#x003E; </span>pdflatex.
                                                                                         
                                                                                         
<!--l. 18137--><p class="noindent" >Information about Lua is available at http://www.lua.org .
