<!--l. 18517--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">mif </span>terminal driver produces Frame Maker MIF format version 3.00. It plots in MIF Frames with the size
15*10 cm, and plot primitives with the same pen will be grouped in the same MIF group. Plot primitives in a
<span 
class="cmbx-10">gnuplot </span>page will be plotted in a MIF Frame, and several MIF Frames are collected in one large MIF Frame. The
MIF font used for text is <span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>Times<span 
class="cmtt-10">"</span>.
