<!--l. 20369--><p class="noindent" >
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-476000IV"></a>VWS</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-947"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-476001"></a>
<!--l. 20378--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">VWS </span>terminal driver supports the VAX Windowing System. It has no options. It will sense the display type
(monochrome, gray scale, or color.) All line styles are plotted as solid lines.
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a 
 id="x1-477000IV"></a>Vx384</h4>
<a 
 id="Q1-1-949"></a>
<a 
 id="dx1-477001"></a>
<!--l. 20390--><p class="noindent" >The <span 
class="cmbx-10">vx384 </span>terminal driver supports the Vectrix 384 and Tandy color printers. It has no options.
